  },
  {
    "number": 3,
    "title": "Runaway Pop Star",
    "overview": "With the power of magic at their disposal, Ari and her friends think they can solve everyone's problems easier. Then one day, the show 'Pop Music Now' comes to broadcast live at the outdoor stage beside their school. While rehearsing, pop star legend Lyla starts to emit Hopeless Energy which attracts Trump and Mao. Eventually, Tubby and Trump run into each other...",
